docs {
  # OAuth Login
  
  Open this URL in your browser to login with GitHub.
  After successful login, you'll be redirected to the frontend with a token.
  
  The token will be stored in localStorage. You can get it from the browser console:
  ```
  localStorage.getItem('token')
  ```
  
  Then paste it into the environment variable 'token'.
}
